ğŸ“Œ Project Overview

Email spam detection is a critical application of machine learning that helps filter unwanted and potentially harmful messages.
This project focuses on building a Spam Email Detection system using machine learning classification algorithms to accurately classify emails as Spam or Not Spam (Ham) based on their content.

The model is trained on labeled email data and uses text processing techniques combined with a robust classifier to achieve high accuracy.

